###
// GET - Lista todos os usuários
GET {{baseURL}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
// GET - Lista o usuário pelo ID
GET {{baseURL}}/{{id}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
